                    <span>The Monsters of Morley Manor is an excellent book for young readers and old readers alike. I didn't find a lot of books I wanted to read, but my Mom suggested I read this book and it was like a magic portal to reading land. It was exciting the whole time -- it didn't have a long, slow beginning like some books. It had wonderful characters with great personalities and there is so much spine-tingling adventure in it. If I could have given it more stars, I would give it a million.</span>
                  
